            <content>
                <p>
                    <q>The set of vectors <m>{{vecset}}</m> <em>spans</em> <m>\mathbb R^4</m>.</q>
                </p>
            </content>
        </knowl>
        <knowl>
            <content>
                <p>
                    <q>The set of vectors <m>{{vecset}}</m> does <em>not</em> span <m>\mathbb R^4</m>.</q>
                </p>
            </content>
        </knowl>
    </knowl>
    <knowl>
        <content>
            <p>
Explain how to determine which of these statements is true.
            </p>
        </content>
    </knowl>
